{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. 2 S 15:31-34. Job 5:12-16.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Achitophel dit \u00e0 Absalom: Laisse-moi choisir douze mille hommes! Je me l\u00e8verai, et je poursuivrai David cette nuit m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2","name":"2 Samuel 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23","name":"2 Samuel 16:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Je le surprendrai pendant qu\u2019il est fatigu\u00e9 et que ses mains sont affaiblies, je l\u2019\u00e9pouvanterai, et tout le peuple qui est avec lui s\u2019enfuira. Je frapperai le roi seul,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3","name":"2 Samuel 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1","name":"2 Samuel 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>et je ram\u00e8nerai \u00e0 toi tout le peuple; la mort de l\u2019homme \u00e0 qui tu en veux assurera le retour de tous, et tout le peuple sera en paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4","name":"2 Samuel 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2","name":"2 Samuel 17:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Cette parole plut \u00e0 Absalom et \u00e0 tous les anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5","name":"2 Samuel 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3","name":"2 Samuel 17:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Cependant Absalom dit: Appelez encore Huscha\u00ef, l\u2019Arkien, et que nous entendions aussi ce qu\u2019il dira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6","name":"2 Samuel 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4","name":"2 Samuel 17:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Huscha\u00ef vint aupr\u00e8s d\u2019Absalom, et Absalom lui dit: Voici comment a parl\u00e9 Achitophel: devons-nous faire ce qu\u2019il a dit, ou non? Parle, toi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7","name":"2 Samuel 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5","name":"2 Samuel 17:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Huscha\u00ef r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Absalom: Pour cette fois le conseil qu\u2019a donn\u00e9 Achitophel n\u2019est pas bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8","name":"2 Samuel 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6","name":"2 Samuel 17:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et Huscha\u00ef dit: Tu connais la bravoure de ton p\u00e8re et de ses gens, ils sont furieux comme le serait dans les champs une ourse \u00e0 qui l\u2019on aurait enlev\u00e9 ses petits. Ton p\u00e8re est un homme de guerre, et il ne passera pas la nuit avec le peuple;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9","name":"2 Samuel 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7","name":"2 Samuel 17:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>voici maintenant, il est cach\u00e9 dans quelque fosse ou dans quelque autre lieu. Et si, d\u00e8s le commencement, il en est qui tombent sous leurs coups, on ne tardera pas \u00e0 l\u2019apprendre et l\u2019on dira: Il y a une d\u00e9faite parmi le peuple qui suit Absalom!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10","name":"2 Samuel 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8","name":"2 Samuel 17:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Alors le plus vaillant, e\u00fbt-il un c\u0153ur de lion, sera saisi d\u2019\u00e9pouvante; car tout Isra\u00ebl sait que ton p\u00e8re est un h\u00e9ros et qu\u2019il a des braves avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11","name":"2 Samuel 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9","name":"2 Samuel 17:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Je conseille donc que tout Isra\u00ebl se rassemble aupr\u00e8s de toi, depuis Dan jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Beer-Sch\u00e9ba, multitude pareille au sable qui est sur le bord de la mer. Tu marcheras en personne au combat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12","name":"2 Samuel 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10","name":"2 Samuel 17:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Nous arriverons \u00e0 lui en quelque lieu que nous le trouvions, et nous tomberons sur lui comme la ros\u00e9e tombe sur le sol; et pas un n\u2019\u00e9chappera, ni lui ni aucun des hommes qui sont avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13","name":"2 Samuel 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11","name":"2 Samuel 17:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>S\u2019il se retire dans une ville, tout Isra\u00ebl portera des cordes vers cette ville, et nous la tra\u00eenerons au torrent, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019on n\u2019en trouve plus une pierre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14","name":"2 Samuel 17:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12","name":"2 Samuel 17:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Absalom et tous les gens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dirent: Le conseil de Huscha\u00ef, l\u2019Arkien, vaut mieux que le conseil d\u2019Achitophel. Or l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait r\u00e9solu d\u2019an\u00e9antir le bon conseil d\u2019Achitophel, afin d\u2019amener le malheur sur Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15","name":"2 Samuel 17:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13","name":"2 Samuel 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-23: cf. (2 S 15:35, 36. Jos 2:1-7.) Mt 27:3-5. Ps 55.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Huscha\u00ef dit aux sacrificateurs Tsadok et Abiathar: Achitophel a donn\u00e9 tel et tel conseil \u00e0 Absalom et aux anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; et moi, j\u2019ai conseill\u00e9 telle et telle chose.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16","name":"2 Samuel 17:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14","name":"2 Samuel 17:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Maintenant, envoyez tout de suite informer David et faites-lui dire: Ne passe point la nuit dans les plaines du d\u00e9sert, mais va plus loin, de peur que le roi et tout le peuple qui est avec lui ne soient expos\u00e9s \u00e0 p\u00e9rir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17","name":"2 Samuel 17:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15","name":"2 Samuel 17:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Jonathan et Achimaats se tenaient \u00e0 En-Roguel. Une servante vint leur dire d\u2019aller informer le roi David; car ils n\u2019osaient pas se montrer et entrer dans la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18","name":"2 Samuel 17:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16","name":"2 Samuel 17:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Un jeune homme les aper\u00e7ut, et le rapporta \u00e0 Absalom. Mais ils partirent tous deux en h\u00e2te, et ils arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 Bachurim \u00e0 la maison d\u2019un homme qui avait un puits dans sa cour, et ils y descendirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19","name":"2 Samuel 17:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17","name":"2 Samuel 17:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>La femme prit une couverture qu\u2019elle \u00e9tendit sur l\u2019ouverture du puits, et elle y r\u00e9pandit du grain pil\u00e9 pour qu\u2019on ne se dout\u00e2t de rien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20","name":"2 Samuel 17:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18","name":"2 Samuel 17:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Les serviteurs d\u2019Absalom entr\u00e8rent dans la maison aupr\u00e8s de cette femme, et dirent: O\u00f9 sont Achimaats et Jonathan? La femme leur r\u00e9pondit: Ils ont pass\u00e9 le ruisseau. Ils cherch\u00e8rent, et ne les trouvant pas, ils retourn\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21","name":"2 Samuel 17:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19","name":"2 Samuel 17:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s leur d\u00e9part, Achimaats et Jonathan remont\u00e8rent du puits et all\u00e8rent informer le roi David. Ils dirent \u00e0 David: Levez-vous et h\u00e2tez-vous de passer l\u2019eau, car Achitophel a conseill\u00e9 contre vous telle chose.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22","name":"2 Samuel 17:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20","name":"2 Samuel 17:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>David et tout le peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui se lev\u00e8rent et ils pass\u00e8rent le Jourdain; \u00e0 la lumi\u00e8re du matin, il n\u2019y en avait pas un qui f\u00fbt rest\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9cart, pas un qui n\u2019e\u00fbt pass\u00e9 le Jourdain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23","name":"2 Samuel 17:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21","name":"2 Samuel 17:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Achitophel, voyant que son conseil n\u2019\u00e9tait pas suivi, sella son \u00e2ne et partit pour s\u2019en aller chez lui dans sa ville. Il donna ses ordres \u00e0 sa maison, et il s\u2019\u00e9trangla. C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019il mourut, et on l\u2019enterra dans le s\u00e9pulcre de son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24","name":"2 Samuel 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22","name":"2 Samuel 17:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.025,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">David \u00e0 Mahana\u00efm, au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain; Absalom \u00e0 sa poursuite<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 24-29: cf. (Ps 4; 42; 43; 61; 63.) 2 S 19:31-39.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>David arriva \u00e0 Mahana\u00efm. Et Absalom passa le Jourdain, lui et tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25","name":"2 Samuel 17:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23","name":"2 Samuel 17:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Absalom mit Amasa \u00e0 la t\u00eate de l\u2019arm\u00e9e, en remplacement de Joab; Amasa \u00e9tait fils d\u2019un homme appel\u00e9 Jithra, l\u2019Isra\u00e9lite, qui \u00e9tait all\u00e9 vers Abigal, fille de Nachasch et s\u0153ur de Tseruja, m\u00e8re de Joab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26","name":"2 Samuel 17:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24","name":"2 Samuel 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Isra\u00ebl et Absalom camp\u00e8rent dans le pays de Galaad.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27","name":"2 Samuel 17:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25","name":"2 Samuel 17:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:27","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Lorsque David fut arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 Mahana\u00efm, Schobi, fils de Nachasch, de Rabba des fils d\u2019Ammon, Makir, fils d\u2019Ammiel, de Lodebar, et Barzilla\u00ef, le Galaadite, de Roguelim,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28","name":"2 Samuel 17:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26","name":"2 Samuel 17:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:28","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>apport\u00e8rent des lits, des bassins, des vases de terre, du froment, de l\u2019orge, de la farine, du grain r\u00f4ti, des f\u00e8ves, des lentilles, des pois r\u00f4tis,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29","name":"2 Samuel 17:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27","name":"2 Samuel 17:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 17:29","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.17.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>du miel, de la cr\u00e8me, des brebis, et des fromages de vache. Ils apport\u00e8rent ces choses \u00e0 David et au peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui, afin qu\u2019ils mangeassent; car ils disaient: Ce peuple a d\u00fb souffrir de la faim, de la fatigue et de la soif, dans le d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17","name":"2 Samuel 17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1","name":"2 Samuel 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28","name":"2 Samuel 17:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb54224c2.85649753');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb54224c2.85649753\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb54224c2.85649753","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb54224c2.85649753'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb54224c2.85649753\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}